After Barcelona took a giant step towards winning the La Liga title with a 2-1 win in El Clasico on Sunday night the squad looked ready to celebrate in style - except Lionel Messi that is.

While team-mates including Neymar Jnr, Dani Alves, and Adriano got suited and booted in their garish designer suits, the Argentina forward opted for a more conservative look.

On the pitch Messi has the ability  to set the place alight but his ensemble on Sunday night left him looking distinctly average in comparison to his South American team-mates.

